  m_text: "Welcome to Assistive Creative Design, an AI-powered poster creation platform
    designed for blind and visually impaired participants.\n\nHOW TO USE\n\n1. Enter
    participant information.\n\u2022 Fill in your name, institution, and category.\n\u2022
    You may type using the keyboard or use the microphone button for voice input.\n\n2.
    Create a poster prompt.\n\u2022Describe your poster idea using text or voice.\n\u2022Press
    Generate Poster to create an AI-generated poster image.\n"
